The paper discusses a new approach to Transfer Learning in Reinforcement Learning, which involves adapting and reusing the mapped source task optimal-policy directly in related domains. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper deals with Reinforcement Learning, which is a subfield of Robotics (cs.RO) and Systems and Control (cs.SY). The paper also mentions sample efficiency and reducing sample complexity, which suggests that it may be relevant to Computer Vision (cs.CV) as well.
